The '''''Line of Elros''''' was a document that listed the names of the [[King of Númenor|Kings]] and [[Ruling Queen of Númenor|Queens]] of [[Númenor]], and contained a brief account of their birthdate, length of rule, death date, and a summary of events that occurred during their reigns. The ''Line of Elros'' was probably made in [[Middle-earth]] (most likely in [[Gondor]]) after the [[Downfall of Númenor]], as it contains a reference to [[Elendil]]'s writing of the ''[[Akallabêth]]'', which is an account of that disaster.
